Package com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models

Class Assignment

java.lang.Object
com.osoc6.OSOC6.database.models.Assignment
@Entity public class Assignment extends Object
The database entity for an Assignment. An Assignment is the registration of a user assigning a Student on a Project. The assignment can be invalid, this means the assignment was performed but is no longer looked at. The assignment can be non-suggestive, this means the project of this assignment has been locked. Every assignment has a reason.
